      <title>美国认为乌克兰可以占领俄罗斯领土数月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/us-believes-that-ukraine-can-hold-russian-territory-for-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美国高级官员称，美国评估乌克兰将能够守住其在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区占领的领土至少几个月，甚至更长时间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/us-believes-that-ukraine-can-hold-russian-territory-for-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Oct 2024 21:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
